rows.label: bf05120100_0005
rows.name: Rex!

rows.label: bf05120100_0010
rows.name:
Whoa, Kirk? Kazuna? You guys
sure have grown!

rows.label: bf05120100_0020
rows.name: And hey, is that really-

rows.label: bf05120100_0030
rows.name: That's our Martis.

rows.label: bf05120100_0040
rows.name:
He'll be going away to school in Acedia soon,
thanks to the help you've been sending us.

rows.label: bf05120100_0050
rows.name: Auntie Correl, good to see you!

rows.label: bf05120100_0060
rows.name: Wow, this is quite a welcome...

rows.label: bf05120100_0070
rows.name:
I didn't realize you were sending your
money home.

rows.label: bf05120100_0080
rows.name:
That's very admirable for such a young
man.

rows.label: bf05120100_0090
rows.name: Home, huh...

rows.label: bf05120100_0100
rows.name: Old lady have lots of littlepons!

rows.label: bf05120100_0110
rows.name:
Masterpon, these clearly not all
littlepons of same parent.

rows.label: bf05120100_0120
rows.name: My word! Is that old Seiryuu there?

rows.label: bf05120100_0130
rows.name:
What have you gone and done
to yourself?

rows.label: bf05120100_0140
rows.name: That would take some explaining.

rows.label: bf05120100_0150
rows.name:
Incidentally...
Is there some way you could put us up for the night?

rows.label: bf05120100_0160
rows.name: Long day and all.

rows.label: bf05120100_0170
rows.name:
"Is there some way?" Don't give me
that!

rows.label: bf05120100_0180
rows.name: Stay for as long as you like! What's mine is yours.

rows.label: bf05120100_0190
rows.name: Thank you.

rows.label: bf05120100_0200
rows.name:
Auntie, thank you so much.
I think I'll go for a bit of a walk first, though.

rows.label: bf05120100_0210
rows.name:
Ah, yes.
Leave your friends with me.

rows.label: bf05120100_0220
rows.name: Homura, could you come along too?

rows.label: bf05120100_0230
rows.name:
Hm?
O-of course.

rows.label: bf05120100_0240
rows.name: Right then, come with me, all of you!
